The elite guard of the Mesa High Priests, the Ivory Guardians were created to protect the innocent and faithful.
The elite guard of the Mesa High Priests, the Ivory Guardians, were created to protect the innocent and faithful. Some say their actions are above the law.

name: Ivory Mask
text: You have shroud. (You can't be the target of spells or abilities.)

editions.flavor: Made from its wearer's hopes, the mask ensures that those hopes will be fulfilled.
"I did not choose my role, Orim," said Cho-Manno patiently, "and I suspect Gerrard did not choose his."
